{"article_id":"8RYTJd2T6Ayu6wr3","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The FBI shocked the political world on Friday","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"by announcing","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"that newly discovered emails have caused the bureau to renew its inquiry into Hillary Clinton ' s private email server .","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"The Clinton campaign has for months thought","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"the worst of the email server controversy was over .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"In July , to their great relief , FBI Director James Comey said","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"that Clinton would not face criminal charges","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"for sending emails over a private server while secretary of state .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"But whatever new emails","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"authorities have found","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"are apparently enough","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"to trigger a second look","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"at whether she broke the law .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"Comey ' s letter to Congress on Friday doesn ' t say much ,","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"but it does at least suggest","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"that the FBI is still looking into","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"whether Clinton violated federal law","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"by sending classified email over her private server .","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"( Comey said","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"the FBI had come across new emails in \" an unrelated case , \"","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"and that the bureau will review them","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"\" to determine","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"whether they contain classified information ,","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"as well as to assess their importance to our investigation \" into Clinton . )","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"There ' s a lot we don ' t know yet .","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"But ,","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"citing anonymous sources ,","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"multiple news outlets have reported","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"that these emails are from \" a device \"","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"belonging to Clinton aide Huma Abedin and her husband Anthony Weiner","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"and were discovered via an unrelated investigation .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"Of course , the new line of investigation does not necessarily mean","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"that Clinton broke the law .","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"With less than two weeks until the election , Comey ' s letter to Congress will lead to ferocious new partisan attacks over her private server .","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"( Donald Trump is already making them . )","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"We have no more proof","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"that Clinton broke the law today","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"than we did yesterday .","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"All","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"we know","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"is that Comey has new records","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"he thinks","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"are worthy of further investigation .","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"That said ,","depth":4},{"id":44,"text":"it ' s important to be clear about just why Clinton ' s email server is now one of the biggest stories of the 2016 presidential campaign .","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"And to understand that ,","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"you have to understand why she was under investigation in the first place .","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"One of the big challenges","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"in writing about the \" Hillary Clinton email controversy \"","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"is that it ' s one overly broad category","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"that ' s being used","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"to capture several distinct accusations against the Democratic presidential nominee .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"The shorthand \" Hillary ' s emails , \"","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"though somewhat irresistible ,","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"suggests a single controversy","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"that is somehow both monolithic and strangely sprawling .","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"The reality is that there are actually four","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"( or ,","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"if you include claims of a cover-up ,","depth":13},{"id":59,"text":"five ;","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"or ,","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"if you include Benghazi ,","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"six )","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"distinct controversies","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"that involve both Clinton and email .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"Indeed , there are several separate groups of emails ,","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"and some of the accusations against Clinton are contradictory .","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"To understand what ' s happening ,","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"it ' s useful to split up these controversies","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"rather than lump them together :","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"One controversy","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"related to Clinton ' s emails","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"is that she exchanged classified information over a private server","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"that was susceptible to hacking by foreign agents .","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"This is an issue about cybersecurity -","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"that Clinton didn ' t do enough","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"to safeguard government secrets .","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"This is what the FBI ' s investigation is about ,","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"and what appears to be behind Comey ' s new investigation .","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"The FBI has discovered a new set of emails","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"- apparently emerging from its separate inquiry into Anthony Weiner -","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"that is making it look again at this question","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"of whether Clinton broke a law .","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"Another claim is that Clinton ' s private server allowed her to avoid public records laws .","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"This is a controversy","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"related to the idea of transparency -","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"that government officials have to keep records of their work ,","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"and that Clinton deliberately avoided doing so .","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"Separately , emails from Clinton ' s aides have also fed into different controversies about the Clinton Foundation and the Benghazi compound attack .","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"At heart , these stories are about donor access and foreign policy .","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"More recently , there ' s also the internal Clinton campaign emails","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"revealed by WikiLeaks .","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"These , generally speaking , have nothing to do with any of the emails above .","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"It ' s crucial to separate these investigations in your head","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"to understand the significance of the FBI ' s investigation .","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"The FBI was mostly concerned","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"- and ,","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"according to today ' s announcement ,","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"remains concerned -","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"that Clinton took risks","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"by using a private server","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"to expose state secrets","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"that could be obtained by malicious foreign actors .","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"In July , the FBI said","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"its investigation into Clinton looked at","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"whether \" classified information was improperly stored or transmitted on ( her ) personal system , in violation of a federal statute","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"making it a felony to mishandle classified information either intentionally or in a grossly negligent way , \"","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"or if she broke a second law","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"making it illegal to \" knowingly remove classified information from appropriate systems or storage facilities. \"","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"We have no idea","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"if the new emails will provide evidence of that ,","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"but it appears to be what the FBI will be looking at .","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"It ' s not in dispute that Clinton used a private email account and a `` homebrew '' private email server exclusively during her four years as secretary of state .","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"In doing so ,","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"she wound up exchanging emails","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"containing classified information","depth":13},{"id":116,"text":"over communications systems","depth":13},{"id":117,"text":"that did not have the safeguards of the government .","depth":13},{"id":118,"text":"In all , Clinton sent or received more than 100 emails","depth":13},{"id":119,"text":"considered classified","depth":13},{"id":120,"text":"- seven of which were marked `` top secret '' -","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"on the private server","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"installed in her family ' s home in Westchester , New York .","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"The FBI ' s investigation ,","depth":14},{"id":124,"text":"the records of which were released in September in a 58-page report ,","depth":14},{"id":125,"text":"makes clear","depth":13},{"id":126,"text":"there ' s no direct proof","depth":13},{"id":127,"text":"that `` hostile agents '' penetrated Clinton ' s private server .","depth":13},{"id":128,"text":"And","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"as ' s Dylan Matthews has noted ,","depth":14},{"id":130,"text":"prosecutors would need evidence","depth":15},{"id":131,"text":"not just that Clinton sent classified information outside secure government networks","depth":16},{"id":132,"text":"but that she did so","depth":17},{"id":133,"text":"knowing","depth":18},{"id":134,"text":"that it was supposed to be classified .","depth":18},{"id":135,"text":"That ' s the standard","depth":14},{"id":136,"text":"the FBI needs","depth":14},{"id":137,"text":"to prove","depth":14},{"id":138,"text":"Clinton broke the law .","depth":14},{"id":139,"text":"Clinton has denied this ,","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"insisting","depth":13},{"id":141,"text":"that any classified material in the emails was classified after the fact","depth":14},{"id":142,"text":"or she did not realize","depth":15},{"id":143,"text":"it had been classified .","depth":15},{"id":144,"text":"And the FBI had cleared Clinton of the charge","depth":13},{"id":145,"text":"that she had knowingly sent classified information .","depth":13},{"id":146,"text":"But even short of committing a crime ,","depth":13},{"id":147,"text":"Comey has also made clear","depth":14},{"id":148,"text":"that Clinton ' s private server made it more vulnerable to foreign hackers ,","depth":15},{"id":149,"text":"that outside actors repeatedly tried to break into her email account ,","depth":16},{"id":150,"text":"and that exchanging classified email over private servers at all was `` extremely careless . ''","depth":16},{"id":151,"text":"Trump has suggested","depth":13},{"id":152,"text":"that China and/or Russia have actually obtained Clinton ' s emails .","depth":13},{"id":153,"text":"That is , characteristically , a dramatic overstatement of the facts .","depth":12},{"id":154,"text":"But the claim","depth":14},{"id":155,"text":"that Clinton ' s decision","depth":16},{"id":156,"text":"to use a private server","depth":16},{"id":157,"text":"really did give foreign hackers a greater opportunity","depth":16},{"id":158,"text":"to find classified information","depth":16},{"id":159,"text":"is hard to dismiss out of hand .","depth":13},{"id":160,"text":"As ' s Timothy Lee has written ,","depth":13},{"id":161,"text":"hackers are really good at covering their tracks","depth":14},{"id":162,"text":"if they don ' t want to be discovered .","depth":14},{"id":163,"text":"The New York Times interviewed several cybersecurity experts in July ,","depth":11},{"id":164,"text":"and they all concluded","depth":12},{"id":165,"text":"that it was probable Clinton ' s server was indeed hacked .","depth":12},{"id":166,"text":"There have been three main defenses to this line of criticism .","depth":8},{"id":167,"text":"The first is that much of the `` classified '' information","depth":12},{"id":168,"text":"exchanged","depth":12},{"id":169,"text":"almost certainly didn ' t actually risk exposing national security secrets .","depth":11},{"id":170,"text":"That ' s because the US government has a notoriously broad classification system","depth":12},{"id":171,"text":"that treats anodyne information","depth":14},{"id":172,"text":"( or information","depth":15},{"id":173,"text":"that ' s already public )","depth":15},{"id":174,"text":"as secret .","depth":13},{"id":175,"text":"`` My standard joke is that the NSA is so crazy","depth":14},{"id":176,"text":"they classify their lunch menu , ''","depth":14},{"id":177,"text":"says James Lewis of the Center for Strategic and International Studies in Washington .","depth":13},{"id":178,"text":"`` Was it a bad idea to set up a private server ?","depth":14},{"id":179,"text":"Probably .","depth":14},{"id":180,"text":"Did it hurt national security","depth":15},{"id":181,"text":"or cause any real damage ?","depth":15},{"id":182,"text":"We certainly can ' t conclude that . ''","depth":14},{"id":183,"text":"The second defense ,","depth":13},{"id":184,"text":"noted to me in an email by Steven Aftergood of the Project on Government Secrecy ,","depth":13},{"id":185,"text":"is that the State Department server may not really have been that much safer than the private servers .","depth":12},{"id":186,"text":"After all , State 's own servers were successfully breached in 2006 and then again in 2015 -","depth":12},{"id":187,"text":"so maybe Clinton 's emails were actually safer on the private server ?","depth":12},{"id":188,"text":"The third defense is also persuasive :","depth":11},{"id":189,"text":"Private accounts are pretty routine for government officials .","depth":12},{"id":190,"text":"A 2009 email","depth":17},{"id":191,"text":"sent by then-Secretary of State Colin Powell ,","depth":17},{"id":192,"text":"released Wednesday ,","depth":16},{"id":193,"text":"suggests","depth":15},{"id":194,"text":"that Powell frequently used a private server","depth":16},{"id":195,"text":"to communicate with foreign governments .","depth":16},{"id":196,"text":"( Powell ' s private server wasn ' t a `` homebrew , ''","depth":16},{"id":197,"text":"but it was still outside the government ' s systems . )","depth":16},{"id":198,"text":"Critics have correctly said","depth":15},{"id":199,"text":"that Clinton ' s use of her server appeared to go further than that of other government officials ,","depth":15},{"id":200,"text":"but the Powell revelation makes this controversy look like a broader indictment of a broken email system","depth":15},{"id":201,"text":"- with Clinton being singled out unfairly as a particularly bad example .","depth":15},{"id":202,"text":"Those defenses may be persuasive on the merits .","depth":2},{"id":203,"text":"But they ' re so complicated","depth":3},{"id":204,"text":"that they ' ll probably be tough to make convincing with less than two weeks left in the campaign .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":409,"left":406,"right":408,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":406,"left":247,"right":405,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":247,"left":207,"right":246,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":207,"left":0,"right":206,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":206,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":246,"left":216,"right":245,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":216,"left":211,"right":215,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":211,"left":208,"right":210,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":208,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":210,"left":5,"right":209,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":209,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":215,"left":212,"right":214,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":212,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":214,"left":10,"right":213,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":213,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":245,"left":233,"right":244,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":233,"left":226,"right":232,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":226,"left":220,"right":225,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":220,"left":13,"right":219,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":219,"left":14,"right":218,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":218,"left":15,"right":217,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":217,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":225,"left":18,"right":224,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":224,"left":19,"right":223,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":223,"left":20,"right":222,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":222,"left":221,"right":23,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":221,"left":21,"right":22,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":232,"left":24,"right":231,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":231,"left":228,"right":230,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":228,"left":25,"right":227,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":227,"left":26,"right":27,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":230,"left":229,"right":30,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":229,"left":28,"right":29,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":244,"left":234,"right":243,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":234,"left":31,"right":32,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":243,"left":235,"right":242,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":235,"left":33,"right":34,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":242,"left":237,"right":241,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":237,"left":236,"right":37,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":236,"left":35,"right":36,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":241,"left":238,"right":240,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":238,"left":38,"right":39,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":240,"left":40,"right":239,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":239,"left":41,"right":42,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":405,"left":250,"right":404,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":250,"left":43,"right":249,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":249,"left":44,"right":248,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":248,"left":45,"right":46,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":404,"left":295,"right":403,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":295,"left":269,"right":294,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":269,"left":258,"right":268,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":258,"left":254,"right":257,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":254,"left":251,"right":253,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":251,"left":47,"right":48,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":253,"left":49,"right":252,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":252,"left":50,"right":51,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":257,"left":255,"right":256,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":255,"left":52,"right":53,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":256,"left":54,"right":55,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":268,"left":266,"right":267,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":266,"left":56,"right":265,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":265,"left":264,"right":64,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":264,"left":263,"right":63,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":263,"left":260,"right":262,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":260,"left":57,"right":259,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":259,"left":58,"right":59,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":262,"left":60,"right":261,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":261,"left":61,"right":62,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":267,"left":65,"right":66,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":294,"left":289,"right":293,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":289,"left":271,"right":288,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":271,"left":67,"right":270,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":270,"left":68,"right":69,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":288,"left":283,"right":287,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":283,"left":277,"right":282,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":277,"left":274,"right":276,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":274,"left":272,"right":273,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":272,"left":70,"right":71,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":273,"left":72,"right":73,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":276,"left":74,"right":275,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":275,"left":75,"right":76,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":282,"left":278,"right":281,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":278,"left":77,"right":78,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":281,"left":279,"right":280,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":279,"left":79,"right":80,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":280,"left":81,"right":82,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":287,"left":83,"right":286,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":286,"left":84,"right":285,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":285,"left":85,"right":284,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":284,"left":86,"right":87,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":293,"left":290,"right":292,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":290,"left":88,"right":89,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":292,"left":291,"right":92,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":291,"left":90,"right":91,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":403,"left":304,"right":402,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":304,"left":296,"right":303,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":296,"left":93,"right":94,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":303,"left":299,"right":302,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":299,"left":95,"right":298,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":298,"left":96,"right":297,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":297,"left":97,"right":98,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":302,"left":99,"right":301,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":301,"left":100,"right":300,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":300,"left":101,"right":102,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":402,"left":312,"right":401,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":312,"left":309,"right":311,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":309,"left":103,"right":308,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":308,"left":104,"right":307,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":307,"left":305,"right":306,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":305,"left":105,"right":106,"relation":"el